Description: DNS Whitelist System for Educational Environments
 A multi-layer internet access control system using DNS sinkhole,
 iptables firewall, and browser policies. Blocks all domains by
 default, allowing only whitelisted domains.
 .
 Features:
  - DNS sinkhole (dnsmasq)
  - Firewall rules (iptables)
  - Browser policies (Firefox/Chromium)
  - Automatic whitelist updates
  - Health monitoring
  - Captive portal detection
